45
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,412
Xuan Ji.

46
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:57,618
Do you hear me?

47
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,865
Remember.

48
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,733
I’ve had

49
