Si Feng!

64
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:01,719
Si Feng, it’s me Xuan Ji!

65
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,079
I’m back, Si Feng!

66
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:04,649
Si Feng!

67
00:07:04,650 --> 00:07:05,957
Si Feng!

68
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,517
Yuan Lang.

69
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:23,559
You killed my
mother and Si Feng!

70
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:26,261
