No one can stop me!

74
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:40,006
No one can stop me!

75
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:46,959
Ruo Yu!

76
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:50,851
You took everything from me!

77
00:07:50,852 --> 00:07:54,399
You locked up my family,
killed my loved one,

78
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:56,649
