I must succeed!

85
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,841
- Ruo Yu!
- Ruo Yu!

86
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:38,683
Oh no!

87
00:08:38,684 --> 00:08:41,839
I am the ruler of three realms!

88
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:44,914
The ruler of three realms!

89
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:08,599
